summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending page 24-330 of the Seattle Municipal Code (Plat 40W, page 110, official Zoning Map, as adopted by Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property in Block 8, Supplementary Plat of Union Addition to the City of Seattle from RMV 150 to CG (Petition of Heath Printers, C.F. 290836).
